IMAPAccount gomore-gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User jacob@gomore.com
PassCmd "gpg2 -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.emacs.d/.mbsyncpass.gpg"
Port 993
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs *
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gomore-gmail-imap
Account gomore-gmail

MaildirStore gomore-gmail-local
Path ~/email/mbsyncmail/
Inbox ~/email/mbsyncmail/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel gomore-gmail-channel
Far :gomore-gmail-imap:
Near :gomore-gmail-local:
Patterns *
Create Near
Remove Near
Sync All
Expunge None
SyncState *
MaxMessages 1000
ExpireUnread yes
